“You don’t need objection handling. You need belief detection.”

🔁 THE SALES LOOP: Shift Beliefs → Present Path → Repeat
Sales is just moving in this loop:
1. Diagnose → Which belief isn’t there?
2. Ask a question or share proof to shift it
3. Let them respond. Watch for belief confirmation
4. Only present the offer when all 3 are locked in


