🔁 THE IDENTITY SHIFT LOOP
We maps it like this:
1. Old Identity → Struggling, invisible, hustling
2. New Identity → In control, in demand, respected
3. Your Offer → The bridge between the two
If your sales process doesn’t explicitly highlight this shift, it becomes just another feature list.
